  "title": "Lesson 45: The Power of the Press",
  "audio": "/audio/nce3/45－The Power of the Press.mp3",
  "image": "/images/coming-soon.png",
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "intro_1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Lesson 45",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 0.17,
      "endTime": 2.25,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Lesson",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "课程，第...课"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The power of the press",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.26,
      "endTime": 9.98
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "Does the writer think the parents were lucky or unlucky to gain prosperity in this way? Why?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 9.99,
      "endTime": 20.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "In democratic countries any efforts to restrict the freedom of the press are rightly condemned.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 20.22,
      "endTime": 28.58,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "However, this freedom can easily be abused.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 28.59,
      "endTime": 33.73,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Stories about people often attract far more public attention than political events.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 33.74,
      "endTime": 40.72
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Though we may enjoy reading about the lives of others,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 40.73,
      "endTime": 44.93,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "it is extremely doubtful whether we would equally enjoy reading about ourselves.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 44.94,
      "endTime": 51.75,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Acting on the contention that facts are sacred,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 51.76,
      "endTime": 56.15,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "reporters can cause untold suffering to individuals by publishing details about their private lives.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 56.16,
      "endTime": 65.82,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Newspapers exert such tremendous influence that they can not only bring about major changes to the lives of ordinary people but can even overthrow a government.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 65.83,
      "endTime": 79.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          },
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The story of a poor family that acquired fame and fortune overnight, dramatically illustrates the power of the press.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 79.22,
      "endTime": 88.29,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "That",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "那个"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The family lived in Aberdeen, a small town of 23, 000 inhabitants in South Dakota.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 88.3,
      "endTime": 96.01
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "As the parents had five children, life was a perpetual struggle against poverty.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 96.02,
      "endTime": 102.11,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Five",
            "pos": "num.",
            "meaning": "五"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They were expecting their sixth child and were faced with even more pressing economic problems.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 102.12,
      "endTime": 109.5,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "If they had only had one more child, the fact would have passed unnoticed.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 109.51,
      "endTime": 115.52
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "They would have continued to struggle against economic odds and would have lived in obscurity.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 115.53,
      "endTime": 122.5
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "But they suddenly became the parents of quintuplets, four girls and a boy, an event which radically changed their lives.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 122.51,
      "endTime": 132.98,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The day after the birth of the five children, an aeroplane arrived in Aberdeen bringing sixty reporters and photographers.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 132.99,
      "endTime": 142.4,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Five",
            "pos": "num.",
            "meaning": "五"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s16",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The rise to fame was swift.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 142.41,
      "endTime": 144.74
    },
    {
      "id": "s17",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Television cameras and newspapers carried the news to everyone in the country.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 144.75,
      "endTime": 150.02
    },
    {
      "id": "s18",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Newspapers and magazines offered the family huge sums for the exclusive rights to publish stories and photographs.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 150.03,
      "endTime": 158.51
    },
    {
      "id": "s19",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Gifts poured in not only from unknown people,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 158.52,
      "endTime": 162.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s20",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "but from baby food and soap manufacturers who wished to advertise their products.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 162.22,
      "endTime": 168.82,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s21",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The old farmhouse the family lived in was to be replaced by a new $500, 000 home.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 168.83,
      "endTime": 176.82,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Old",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "老的，旧的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s22",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "Reporters kept pressing for interviews so lawyers had to be employed to act as spokesmen for the family at press conferences.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 176.83,
      "endTime": 186.83,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s23",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "While the five babies were still quietly sleeping in oxygen tents in a hospital nursery,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 186.84,
      "endTime": 193.57,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Five",
            "pos": "num.",
            "meaning": "五"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s24",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "their parents were paying the price for fame.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 193.58,
      "endTime": 197.26,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s25",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It would never again be possible for them to lead normal lives.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 197.27,
      "endTime": 202.19,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s26",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "They had become the victims of commercialization, for their names had acquired a market value.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 202.2,
      "endTime": 210.24,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s27",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Instead of being five new family members, these children had immediately become a commodity.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 210.25,
      "endTime": 215.25,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Five",
            "pos": "num.",
            "meaning": "五"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
}
